ent-RMCMagazineBootsN70 = Boots! Issue No.70.
    .desc = The only official UNMC magazine, the headline reads “Marine 70, The Future of Warfare.” The article then goes on to detail the plans and implementation of Marine 70, a program designed to help modernize the UNMC for 2170.
ent-RMCMagazineBootsN113 = Boots! Issue No.113.
