ent-RMCMagazineBootsN117 = Boots! Issue No.117.
    .desc = The only official UNMC magazine, the headline reads 'STOP CANNING'. The short paragraph further explains the dangers of marines throwing CN-20 Nerve gas into bathrooms as a prank.
