ent-RMCMagazineBootsN131 = Boots! Issue No.131.
    .desc = The only official UNMC magazine, the headline reads 'NO HOTBOXING'. The following paragraph goes into detail about how the HSDP smoke grenades are not safe for long period inhalation exposure and how hypoxia is a poor way to get high.
ent-RMCMagazineBootsN150 = Boots! Issue No.150.
