ent-RMCMagazineBootsN189 = Boots! Issue No.189.
    .desc = The only official UNMC magazine, the headline reads 'Military Police Edition, those that help marines help themselves!'. As with every copy you have ever seen of Issue 189, someone has taken the time to deface it with crude language and unseemly drawings.
